OL,3,CGatland: 'One of the worst first
OL,4,Chalves of my coaching career'
OL,6,FWarren Gatland says Wales' opener was
OL,7,F"one of the worst" halves of rugby in
OL,8,Fhis coaching career.
OL,10,F"It's probably one of the worst 40-
OL,11,Fminute performances in my whole rugby
OL,12,Fcareer as a coach," he told S4C.
OL,14,FWales lost to Scotland at the
OL,15,FPrincipality Stadium for the first
OL,16,Ftime in over 20 years last night.
OL,18,FThe young side were 27-0 down at half
OL,19,Ftime, with Head Coach Gatland
OL,20,Fdescribing the performance as
OL,21,F"absolutely terrible".
