OL,3,CGatland: 'One of the worst first
OL,4,Chalves of my coaching career'
OL,6,F"We're really disappointed with the
OL,7,Ffirst half, we had no tempo, we
OL,8,Fweren't accurate enough." he said.
OL,10,FBut Wales almost managed to turn it
OL,11,Faround, falling short of a historic
OL,12,Fcomeback to end the match 26-27.
OL,14,FGatland said his message to the
OL,15,Fplayers at half time was "simple: just
OL,16,Fgo out there and play some rugby."
OL,18,FIt wasn't all bad though, he said the
OL,19,Fside showed "real character" to "keep
OL,20,Ffighting" in the second half.
