OL,3,CGatland: 'One of the worst first
OL,4,Chalves of my coaching career'
OL,6,FWales' new captain Dafydd Jenkins
OL,7,Fechoed this, saying he was "incredibly
OL,8,Fproud of the boys in the second half."
OL,10,F"We could've thrown the towel in but
OL,11,Fwe didn't."
OL,13,FAt 21 years old, he's the second
OL,14,Fyoungest captain of a Welsh Squad,
OL,15,Fbehind Welsh Rugby legend Gareth
OL,16,FEdwards.
OL,18,FHe said although captaining a Six
OL,19,FNations opener was "incredible", it
OL,20,F"doesn't really mean anything if
OL,21,Fyou're not winning."
