OL,3,CGatland: 'One of the worst first
OL,4,Chalves of my coaching career'
OL,6,FAnother of the young side, Rio Dyer
OL,7,Fscored his fifth international trie in
OL,8,Fthe second half push.
OL,10,FHe said the squad spent the first 40
OL,11,Fminutes "in their shell", but
OL,12,Fattitudes changed during the break.
OL,14,F"We've got nothing to lose now, let's
OL,15,Fgo and show what we can actually do"
OL,17,FLooking ahead to their next Six
OL,18,FNations tie against rivals England, he
OL,19,Fsaid Wales need to use the second half
OL,20,Fperformance to "build momentum onto
OL,21,Fnext week."
